title: O'Neill Wake The Line 2011 - Highlights
description: German wonder kid Nico von Lerchenfeld has won the O'Neill Wake the Line World Championships this weekend in Cologne, Germany, ahead of Shawn Watson and Keith Lidberg, in second and third place.
